name: Block Printed Cards - Carbon Garlands
description:
These cards feature a repeated floral motif printed in deep black on an ivory deckle-edged card with envelope. Measuring 5" x 7", each card is blank inside to suit any occasion, or no occasion in particular.

All Rosewater Mercantile cards are block-printed by hand using antique hardwood textile stamps from India and Afghanistan, with water-based inks on 80 lb. Strathmore paper.
